bhop_omniscient

This map is a port from my cs:go bhop map: https://gamebanana.com/maps/200515
For additional information about the map, please check that page.

This port was done mostly by Fugi, I myself only did some last small edits/fixes
The trees were not ported because they were rescaled using the new cs:go hammer model rescale function. They were only present for visual effects and should not influence the gameplay in any way.
